-LRB- EW.com -RRB- -- A `` Firefly '' reunion is coming to Comic-Con .

Science Channel , which airs repeats of the short-lived Fox cult favorite , is hosting a 10-year anniversary panel for the sci-fi show . Creator Joss Whedon and writer Tim Minear along with stars Nathan Fillion , Alan Tudyk , Adam Baldwin , Sean Maher , Michael Fairman are all expected to be on board .

The panel is being held Friday , July 13 at 12:30 p.m.

